assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Projektengagemang Sweden AB (publ) operates as an engineering and architecture consulting firm in Sweden. It offers architecture services, such as house and landscape architecture, interior and lighting design, town planning, visualization, and inspections services; building services, including building design, acoustics, and geotechnics and surveying, as well as energy, environment, and sustainability services; and fire protection and risk management, fire risk management and customer support, underwriting support, sprinkler systems, protection, and inspection services. The company also provides electrical, telecommunications, and safety services comprising electrical, power, and telecommunications and communications engineering services; reserve power and UPS, security, sprinkler and extinguisher, lighting, lifts and transport, electrical and lightning protection, and AV and multimedia systems; and lighting design, inspections, property automation, control and monitoring, estimates, telesystems, fire protection, risk analysis, construction inspections, energy efficiency improvements, thermographing, and network analysis services. In addition, it offers heating, ventilation and air conditioning, and sanitation systems, cooling, medical gases, and control and monitoring services; environmental services; and engages in the buildings construction and community development activities. Further, the company provides project management services comprising managing building projects and work as a consultant for develop operations, which includes project, quality and working environment, and site supervision and project planning management services, as well as inspection and control, concept/idea to project, business development, strategic leadership, and training services. Projektengagemang Sweden AB (publ) was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
